dev:remarks.maml:para:
Gets all the machines with names that begin with "Core"; 
Adds two disk to each one a 20GB fixed disk on Lun 0 and a 127GB dynamic disk on Lun 1.
The disks will share the name of the VM , suffixed with "-OS" and "-Data" respectively.

command:example.dev:code:
ren .\sql.vhd sql-master.vhd
ren .\prt.vhd prt-master.vhd
get-vhdinfo london*.vhd,paris*.vhd | Connect-VHDParent -ParentVHDPath {$_.parentPath -replace "\.vhd","-master.vhd"}
